thread.title: Asia Stock Markets Broadly Extend Global Retreat

author: Kenan Machado
title: Asia Stock Markets Broadly Extend Global Retreat

organizations.name: asia stock markets broadly extend global retreat asian

text:
U.S. stocks rise after stumbling Wednesday Xerox shares jump on deal report Shares in Europe edge lower Gains in shares of energy companies helped push the S&P 500 higher Thursday, as the broad index recovered from its first setback of the year.
The S&P 500 rose 0.2% in early morning trading after snapping Wednesday its longest winning streak to start a year since 1964. The index is up 2.7% after rising seven of the first eight trading sessions of the year.
